data.description:
Welcome to this charming 2-story home in Dacono, CO. This property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The main floor offers a large family room, a spacious kitchen with an abundance of counter and cabinet space, and an informal dining area with gorgeous LVP flooring. The upper level features a large primary bedroom with a walk-in-closet and a 5 piece primary bathroom. You will find two additional bedrooms and a full bath along with an upper level laundry room. The concrete patio overlooking the fully landscaped private backyard makes a great place for summer BBQ's. With its convenient location and stunning mountain views this home is the perfect blend of comfort and style.
 Easy access to I-25 and HWY 85. 30 minutes to downtown Denver.
 New carpet just installed at the end of January. Roof is less than 3 years old. Fresh exterior paint done in August. Water heater was just replaced in December.
